sub_title: Environmental and Sustainability management student at UvA and Student Business Consultant at 180Degrees
summary:
Master student in Environmental and Sustainability management track at the University of Amsterdam and a Student business consultant at 180Degrees. Graduated from Biology (Ecology) and the University of Groningen. Particularly interested in energy, sustainable business development, and green transition! 

Looking for more opportunities where I will be able to learn and demonstrate my skills in a professional environment outside the University.

Previously an Ambassador of the Green Office at the University of Groningen, rewarded with a sustainability certificate. In the past, I collaborated with the educational department of ZOO Ljubljana, the Bachelor writing team, the Ecosia campaign, and I volunteered at AAP (Animal Advocacy and Protection).

Mostly connecting with those whose career is motivating and inspiring me!!!
